# Project Goals

The primary goal of this application is to empower patients by:

1. Bridging the Communication Gap
   - Help patients who struggle to advocate for themselves
   - Provide structured analysis of medical visits
   - Generate relevant follow-up questions

2. Quality of Care Assurance
   - Analyze if adequate care was provided
   - Identify potential missed diagnoses or concerns
   - Recommend second opinions when necessary

3. Medical Documentation Management
   - Organize and analyze medical visit documentation
   - Convert various media types into structured information
   - Make medical information more accessible and understandable

4. Patient Advocacy
   - Guide patients to ask the right questions
   - Help identify when additional medical opinions are needed
   - Provide specific recommendations for specialist consultations